# API Architecture

## Transport Layer Decision

| Where | Use | Import |
|-------|-----|--------|
| `"use client"` components & hooks | `apiAxios` | `@/src/lib/api-helpers` |
| Server Actions (`"use server"`) | `apiClient` | `@/src/lib/api-helpers` |
| Server Components (RSC) | `apiClient` | `@/src/lib/api-helpers` |

**Never** use `apiAxios` inside Server Actions — it sends cookies that aren't available server-side.  
**Never** use raw `fetch()` in client components — always `apiAxios`.

## API Endpoint Constants

All endpoints defined in `lib/url-helpers/api-endpoints.ts`:

```ts
API.AUTH.LOGIN / LOGOUT / VERIFY / REFRESH / CHANGE_PASSWORD
API.LEADS.LIST / BY_ID(id)
API.PROJECTS.LIST / BY_ID(id) / INTERESTS(id)
API.DOCUMENTS.LIST / BY_ID(id)
API.SERVICES.LIST / BY_ID(id)
API.CONTENT.STATS / STATS_BY_ID(id) / METHODOLOGY / METHODOLOGY_BY_ID(id) / SETTINGS(key)
API.TESTIMONIALS.LIST / BY_ID(id)
API.STATS.ROOT / PROJECTS
API.AUDIT.LIST
API.NOTIFICATIONS.STATUS / TEST
API.STORAGE.REQUEST_UPLOAD_URL
```

Never hardcode `/api/...` strings — always `API.*`.

## TanStack Query Pattern (module services)

```ts
// modules/admin/leads/services/leads.service.ts
export const leadsKeys = {
  all: ["leads"] as const,
  list: (params?) => [...leadsKeys.all, "list", params] as const,
};

export function useLeads(params?: ListLeadsParams) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: leadsKeys.list(params),
    queryFn: () => apiAxios.get(API.LEADS.LIST, { params }).then(r => r.data),
  });
}

export function useUpdateLead() {
  const qc = useQueryClient();
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: ({ id, data }) => apiAxios.patch(API.LEADS.BY_ID(id), data).then(r => r.data),
    onSuccess: () => qc.invalidateQueries({ queryKey: leadsKeys.all }),
  });
}
```

## Backend Route Pattern

```ts
// modules/leads/leads.routes.ts — thin HTTP layer only
router.get(ROUTE_PATHS.LEADS.LIST, requireAuth, async (req, res) => {
  const parsed = ListLeadsQuery.safeParse(req.query);
  if (!parsed.success) { res.status(400).json({ error: "Invalid query" }); return; }
  const result = await listLeads(parsed.data);  // service call only
  res.json(result);
});
```

## Zustand — UI State Only

```ts
// ✅ Correct — UI state
const { isModalOpen, setModalOpen } = useModalStore();

// ❌ Wrong — API data in Zustand
const { leads, setLeads } = useLeadsStore(); // Never — use TanStack Query
```
